Subject: [PATCH 01/10] ARM: at91: sama5d3: add definition for usart base
 address

Signed-off-by: Bo Shen <voice.shen@atmel.com>
Signed-off-by: Nicolas Ferre <nicolas.ferre@atmel.com>

Conflicts:
	arch/arm/mach-at91/include/mach/sama5d3.h
---
 arch/arm/mach-at91/include/mach/sama5d3.h | 8 ++++++++
 1 file changed, 8 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/mach-at91/include/mach/sama5d3.h b/arch/arm/mach-at91/include/mach/sama5d3.h
index 90dc1fa..635839d 100644
--- a/arch/arm/mach-at91/include/mach/sama5d3.h
+++ b/arch/arm/mach-at91/include/mach/sama5d3.h
@@ -70,6 +70,14 @@
 #define SAMA5D3_BASE_RTC	0xfffffeb0
 
 /*
+ * User Peripheral physical base addresses.
+ */
+#define SAMA5D3_BASE_USART0	0xf001c000
+#define SAMA5D3_BASE_USART1	0xf0020000
+#define SAMA5D3_BASE_USART2	0xf8020000
+#define SAMA5D3_BASE_USART3	0xf8024000
+
+/*
  * Internal Memory
  */
 #define SAMA5D3_SRAM_BASE	0x00300000	/* Internal SRAM base address */
